{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01GQJMcbWaBkqWKCbDHUSseE","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→Feature: Docs Change Run Start Orchestration\n     2→  The `run start` command executes the `docs_change` preset on the shared\n     3→  workflow engine, persisting canonical payloads, rendered artifacts, journal\n     4→  events, and run snapshots at each durable stage boundary.\n     5→\n     6→  # SC-DOCS-START-001\n     7→  Scenario: Happy path docs_change run completes all stages\n     8→    Given an initialized workspace with project \"docs-alpha\" using flow \"docs_change\"\n     9→    And project \"docs-alpha\" is selected as active\n    10→    And the run snapshot shows status \"not_started\" with no active run\n    11→    When the user runs \"run start\"\n    12→    Then the command exits successfully\n    13→    And the run snapshot shows status \"completed\" with no active run\n    14→    And the journal records \"docs_plan\", \"docs_update\", \"docs_validation\", and \"review\" in sequence\n    15→    And payload and artifact records exist for all 4 docs_change stages\n    16→\n    17→  # SC-DOCS-START-002\n    18→  Scenario: Docs validation request_changes restarts from docs_update\n    19→    Given an initialized workspace with project \"docs-bravo\" using flow \"docs_change\"\n    20→    And project \"docs-bravo\" is selected as active\n    21→    And the docs_validation stage first returns \"request_changes\" with follow-up amendment \"fix the broken link targets\"\n    22→    When the user runs \"run start\"\n    23→    Then the command exits successfully\n    24→    And the journal contains a \"cycle_advanced\" event from cycle 1 to cycle 2 resuming at \"docs_update\"\n    25→    And the docs_update stage is entered twice across the run\n    26→    And the second docs_update invocation includes the docs_validation follow-up amendment in its remediation context\n    27→\n    28→  # SC-DOCS-START-003\n    29→  Scenario: Docs validation rejected fails the run\n    30→    Given an initialized workspace with project \"docs-charlie\" using flow \"docs_change\"\n    31→    And project \"docs-charlie\" is selected as active\n    32→    And the docs_validation stage returns \"rejected\"\n    33→    When the user runs \"run start\"\n    34→    Then the command fails with error containing \"docs_validation\"\n    35→    And the journal ends with a \"run_failed\" event referencing \"docs_validation\"\n    36→    And the run snapshot shows status \"failed\" with no active run\n    37→\n    38→  # SC-DOCS-START-004\n    39→  Scenario: Retryable docs_update transport failure succeeds on a later attempt\n    40→    Given an initialized workspace with project \"docs-delta\" using flow \"docs_change\"\n    41→    And project \"docs-delta\" is selected as active\n    42→    And the docs_update stage fails once with a transport failure before succeeding\n    43→    When the user runs \"run start\"\n    44→    Then the command exits successfully\n    45→    And the journal contains a \"stage_failed\" event for \"docs_update\" with will_retry true\n    46→    And the docs_update stage is entered twice with attempts 1 and 2\n    47→\n    48→  # SC-DOCS-START-005\n    49→  Scenario: Conditionally approved docs validation preserves follow-up amendments in snapshot state\n    50→    Given an initialized workspace with project \"docs-echo\" using flow \"docs_change\"\n    51→    And project \"docs-echo\" is selected as active\n    52→    And the docs_validation stage returns \"conditionally_approved\" with follow-up amendment \"add a rollout caveat\"\n    53→    When the user runs \"run start\"\n    54→    Then the command exits successfully\n    55→    And the run snapshot shows status \"completed\" with no active run\n    56→    And the amendment_queue pending list in run.json is empty\n    57→    And the run snapshot records the docs_validation follow-up amendment without a completion-round restart\n    58→    And no \"amendment_queued\" or \"completion_round_advanced\" events exist\n    59→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01JZgEXfVjTEVJPd1ayi2jcT","session_id":"d6d77a57-6575-434e-8636-d856c1e7216a","uuid":"2e8df74e-a83f-4b97-a4af-33b20f2931c6"}
